    <div class="attraction">
      <h3>Sagrada Familia</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> A Basilica in Barcelona, designed by Antoni Gaudí. The building's unique architecture and stunning stained-glass windows make it a must-see.</p>
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558560354-c17a5af844d6?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w3NTA3Njl8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxTYWdyYWRhJTIwRmFtaWxpYXxlbnwwfHx8fDE3NDc1NzU0NTB8MA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080" alt="Sagrada Familia" loading="lazy" />
